OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather wet start this morning
OL,6,Fwith a band of rain breaking up into
OL,7,Fshowers before easing throughout the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Some of the showers will be
OL,9,Fheavy, but some sunnier interludes
OL,10,Fdeveloping in between. Temperatures
OL,11,Fstill a little below average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome late spells of sunshine
OL,14,Faround this evening, before a band of
OL,15,Frain and blustery winds spread in
OL,16,Fovernight. A milder night than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
